channel.title: Definition of Coding(?)
channel.description:
Ive heard so many different definitions. I think it just means able to make stuff in the private server, not java. I know alot of people who are good coders but don't even mess with booleans or voids. [code]The process of converting information obtained on a subject or unit into coded values[/code]
I just wanted to know what you guys thought about it.
